aterial as evidence. \n\nWith an innovative combination of a motivated local community, law and technology, SPDA has already successfully intervened on several occasions to stop illegal loggers in the act. All this supports collaboration amongst local communities for improving the safety of Environmental Defenders.', '0', '1');
